
### Register User.
POST http://localhost:8000/api/users/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test1@gmail.com",
  "username": "test1",
  "password": "1234"
}

### GET Tokens

POST http://localhost:8000/api/token/
Content-Type: application/json

 {
    "email":"test1@gmail.com",
    "password":"1234"
 }